<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 08:10:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国参议院通过法案向以色列提供数十亿美元援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/u-s-senate-passes-bill-providing-billions-in-aid-to-israel/0000018f-0e69-d0a8-a5ef-bf6dfd190000</link><description>众议院周六批准该方案后，该法案以 79 票对 18 票的压倒性通过。拜登总统表示，今晚，参议院两党多数派与众议院一起响应历史在这个关键转折点的号召。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:58:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/u-s-senate-passes-bill-providing-billions-in-aid-to-israel/0000018f-0e69-d0a8-a5ef-bf6dfd190000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯高级官员：我们提出在第一阶段协议中释放40名人质；辛瓦尔参观隧道外</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article-live/u-s-senate-passes-bill-providing-billions-in-aid-to-israel/0000018f-0ddd-d6a0-a9ef-cddd5c300000</link><description>哥伦比亚大学午夜向学生抗议者发出最后通牒，要求拆除营地通行证 ■ 数百名抗议者封锁特拉维夫以色列国防军总部外的道路，呼吁释放人质 ■ 以色列国防军宣布预备役士兵在加沙战斗中丧生 ■ 以色列国防军命令加沙北部拜特拉希亚的居民，撤离</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 03:14:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article-live/u-s-senate-passes-bill-providing-billions-in-aid-to-israel/0000018f-0ddd-d6a0-a9ef-cddd5c300000</guid></item><item><title>辛贝特官员担心以色列监狱长正在放宽犹太安全拘留者的条件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/prisons-chief-easing-jewish-security-inmates-terms/0000018f-0c6f-dc39-a9cf-bdeff5e00000</link><description>这些官员已联系以色列总检察长，表达对国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔的助手、监狱管理局局长科比·雅科比的担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 03:01:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-24/ty-article/.premium/prisons-chief-easing-jewish-security-inmates-terms/0000018f-0c6f-dc39-a9cf-bdeff5e00000</guid></item><item><title>应内塔尼亚胡总理儿子的要求，希伯来语维基百科投票删除有关他的条目</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/hebrew-wikipedia-votes-to-remove-entry-on-pm-netanyahus-son-following-his-request/0000018f-0c51-df8a-afcf-af5b90320000</link><description>本月早些时候，以色列总理之子要求删除阿夫纳·内塔尼亚胡的条目，希伯来语维基百科编辑社区以 75 比 54 的投票结果将阿夫纳·内塔尼亚胡的页面合并到内塔尼亚胡家族的页面中。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 19:18:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/hebrew-wikipedia-votes-to-remove-entry-on-pm-netanyahus-son-following-his-request/0000018f-0c51-df8a-afcf-af5b90320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带北部被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-northern-gaza-strip/0000018f-0c24-df8a-afcf-af3ff5980000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，中士。一等兵（后备）Salm Alkreshat 在周一的战斗行动中在拜特哈农地区阵亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 18:24:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-northern-gaza-strip/0000018f-0c24-df8a-afcf-af3ff5980000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦年长寡妇对美国对以色列军事单位的制裁并不抱太大期望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/palestinian-widow-doesnt-expect-much-from-expected-u-s-sanctions-against-israeli-army/0000018f-0be4-d6a0-a9ef-cbfc82ae0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦和美国双重公民奥马尔·阿卜杜勒马吉德·阿阿德 (Omar Abdalmajeed As&amp;#39;ad) 于 2022 年被以色列军队极端正统派 Netzah Yehuda 部队的成员拘留后死于心脏病，该部队现已受到美国的制裁</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 17:50:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/palestinian-widow-doesnt-expect-much-from-expected-u-s-sanctions-against-israeli-army/0000018f-0be4-d6a0-a9ef-cbfc82ae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 200 天：据报道哈马斯不会接受卡塔尔以外的调解人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-200/0000018f-0bbc-df8a-afcf-afbf8a730001</link><description>卡塔尔表示，对以色列部长攻击其调解努力感到失望，呼吁各国采取行动遏制“以色列对拉法的预期侵略” ■ 据报道，由于盟友的压力，以色列取消了对伊朗进行更广泛袭击的计划 ■ 以色列证实已杀死两名高级官员黎巴嫩真主党成员 ■ 哈马斯呼吁约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人加强对以色列的抵抗行动 ■ 战争 200 天后您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 16:42:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-200/0000018f-0bbc-df8a-afcf-afbf8a730001</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队否认在加沙挖掘万人坑的说法，并称其搜寻人质尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/israeli-army-denies-claim-it-dug-mass-grave-in-gaza-says-it-searched-for-hostages-bodies/0000018f-09da-d6a0-a9ef-c9de6bea0000</link><description>哈马斯声称在汗尤尼斯纳赛尔医院附近的万人坑中发现了数百具尸体，并将责任归咎于以色列国防军 ■ 以色列国防军强烈否认这一指控，称其“毫无根据”</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 15:32:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/israeli-army-denies-claim-it-dug-mass-grave-in-gaza-says-it-searched-for-hostages-bodies/0000018f-09da-d6a0-a9ef-c9de6bea0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队证实两名真主党高级成员在黎巴嫩被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-confirms-killing-of-two-senior-hezbollah-members-in-lebanon/0000018f-0b4d-d6a0-a9ef-cbddffe40000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，周二被杀的特工来自真主党防空系统和精锐的拉德万部队空中部队，并补充说，三架从黎巴嫩起飞的疑似敌对飞机在以色列北部上空被拦截</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 14:57:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-confirms-killing-of-two-senior-hezbollah-members-in-lebanon/0000018f-0b4d-d6a0-a9ef-cbddffe40000</guid></item><item><title>法院命令以色列-巴勒斯坦遇难者家庭论坛重返学校</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/court-orders-israeli-palestinian-bereaved-families-forum-back-in-to-schools/0000018f-0a2d-db42-a99f-afbf8fe20000</link><description>耶路撒冷地方法院法官亚伯拉罕·鲁宾批评教育部禁止“家长圈 - 家庭论坛”在以色列学校运营，尽管没有对右翼组织对其提出的“指控进行适当的事实审查”</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 13:57:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/court-orders-israeli-palestinian-bereaved-families-forum-back-in-to-schools/0000018f-0a2d-db42-a99f-afbf8fe20000</guid></item><item><title>联合国表示，以色列没有提供证据证明近东救济工程处在加沙的工作人员属于恐怖组织</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/un-says-israel-has-not-provided-proof-that-unrwa-staff-in-gaza-belong-to-terror-groups/0000018f-0866-d0d2-a7bf-7dffd6980000</link><description>对该机构“中立性”的独立审查与对以色列声称 12 名工作人员参与 10 月 7 日袭击的调查是分开进行的</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 05:13:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/un-says-israel-has-not-provided-proof-that-unrwa-staff-in-gaza-belong-to-terror-groups/0000018f-0866-d0d2-a7bf-7dffd6980000</guid></item><item><title>美国参议院通过法案向以色列提供数十亿美元援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article-live/un-says-israel-has-not-provided-proof-of-claims-that-unrwa-employees-belong-to-terror-orgs/0000018f-08b9-db42-a99f-adbfa0390000</link><description>以色列国防军说中士。 42 岁的一等兵 Salm Alkreshat 在周一的战斗中身亡 ■ 布林肯计划访问沙特阿拉伯参加世界经济论坛 ■ 以色列国防军命令加沙北部拜特拉希亚居民撤离 ■ 美国指定两家伊朗公司，四人受到网络制裁 ■ 美国官员称，加沙地区，特别是北部地区，饥荒风险“非常高” ■ 数百名示威者封锁特拉维夫以色列国防军总部外的道路，呼吁释放人质</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 02:40:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article-live/un-says-israel-has-not-provided-proof-of-claims-that-unrwa-employees-belong-to-terror-orgs/0000018f-08b9-db42-a99f-adbfa0390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质的家人在内塔尼亚胡家前举行逾越节家宴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-hold-passover-seder-in-front-of-netanyahus-home/0000018f-06fd-d6a0-a9ef-c6fd1eb30000</link><description>逾越节前夕，数百人呼吁释放凯撒利亚的人质。一名亲戚向内塔尼亚胡呼喊，“在自由的节日里，有 133 名犹太公民被哈马斯囚禁，释放我们，这样我们就能有一位勇敢的领导人来达成协议”</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 21:21:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-hold-passover-seder-in-front-of-netanyahus-home/0000018f-06fd-d6a0-a9ef-c6fd1eb30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军情报主管因 10 月 7 日的失败而辞职，这对其他以色列国防领导人来说变成了沙漏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/resignation-of-idf-intel-chief-over-oct-7-turns-hourglass-for-other-defense-leaders/0000018f-06a0-d682-afcf-16a7bdf10000</link><description>阿哈龙·哈利瓦是哈马斯大屠杀后下台的最高级官员，他无法预测他继续担任以色列军队情报部门负责人会造成多么严重的内部危机，也无法预测他会成为右翼分子的目标极端分子</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 18:47:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/resignation-of-idf-intel-chief-over-oct-7-turns-hourglass-for-other-defense-leaders/0000018f-06a0-d682-afcf-16a7bdf10000</guid></item><item><title>美国不应该制裁一个流氓营，而应该关注内塔尼亚胡和他的部长们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-sanctioning-a-rogue-battalion-the-u-s-should-focus-on-netanyahus-government/0000018f-0507-d6a0-a9ef-c59f68d90000</link><description>如果谴责极端正统的内扎·耶胡达以色列国防军营的“莱希法”涉及约旦河西岸的侵犯人权行为，那么以色列的整个政治梯队都需要承担责任。美国应该明确地说</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 14:27:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-sanctioning-a-rogue-battalion-the-u-s-should-focus-on-netanyahus-government/0000018f-0507-d6a0-a9ef-c59f68d90000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查发现，不到四分之一的以色列犹太人支持在加沙重建定居点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/less-than-quarter-of-israeli-jews-in-favor-of-renewed-settlement-in-gaza-poll-finds/0000018f-0587-d64a-a9af-85efc6e30000</link><description>以色列民主研究所进行的民意调查显示，多数以色列人认为应将加沙控制权交给国际部队，13%的人认为巴勒斯坦权力机构应承担责任</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 12:22:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/less-than-quarter-of-israeli-jews-in-favor-of-renewed-settlement-in-gaza-poll-finds/0000018f-0587-d64a-a9af-85efc6e30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在约旦河西岸难民营的行动造成大规模破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-operation-in-west-bank-refugee-camp-leaves-massive-destruction-in-its-wake/0000018f-0549-db42-a99f-adfff02c0000</link><description>图尔卡姆附近的难民营持续了两天的战斗，导致房屋墙壁坑坑洼洼，污水漫溢到街道上，电力也时断时续。 “这里发生的事情让我想起了 1948 年，”营地居民说道</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 11:55:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-operation-in-west-bank-refugee-camp-leaves-massive-destruction-in-its-wake/0000018f-0549-db42-a99f-adfff02c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军事情报局长因导致 10 月 7 日袭击事件失败而辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-intelligence-chief-resigns-citing-failures-leading-up-to-oct-7-attack/0000018f-0509-db32-a58f-fdaf20b00000</link><description>阿哈龙·哈利瓦少将是第一位因哈马斯屠杀事件而辞职的以色列高级国防官员。他在辞职信中写道：“我将永远背负着战争的可怕负担”</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:28:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-intelligence-chief-resigns-citing-failures-leading-up-to-oct-7-attack/0000018f-0509-db32-a58f-fdaf20b00000</guid></item><item><title>受美国制裁的本·格维尔极右翼顾问试图获取天然气，发现信用卡被冻结</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/far-right-ben-gvir-advisor-sanctioned-by-u-s-tries-to-get-gas-finds-credit-card-blocked/0000018f-0507-d6a0-a9ef-c59f80130000</link><description>周末，本茨·戈普斯坦（Bentzi Gopstein）及其领导的极右组织被列入拜登政府受制裁的极端分子名单。发卡机构CAL表示，发卡公司必须遵守与其相关的法律并采取相应行动</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:16:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/far-right-ben-gvir-advisor-sanctioned-by-u-s-tries-to-get-gas-finds-credit-card-blocked/0000018f-0507-d6a0-a9ef-c59f80130000</guid></item><item><title>以色列自10月7日以来发生的10场自残瘟疫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/this-passover-remember-israels-10-self-inflicted-plagues-since-october-7/0000018f-00d0-d6a0-a9ef-c0dce9dd0000</link><description>从“无战略的瘟疫”到“全面胜利的瘟疫”，自从六个多月前与哈马斯的战争开始以来，以色列领导人给他们的人民带来了一场又一场的瘟疫，而且还看不到结束的迹象</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:39:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/this-passover-remember-israels-10-self-inflicted-plagues-since-october-7/0000018f-00d0-d6a0-a9ef-c0dce9dd0000</guid></item></channel></rss>